page_title: 'Quickstart: Generate images with Azure OpenAI Service and Azure OpenAI Studio'
page_description: Learn how to generate images with Azure OpenAI Service in the DALL-E playground (Preview) in Azure OpenAI Studio.
chunk_content: Go to Azure OpenAI StudioBrowse to Azure OpenAI Studio and sign in with the credentials associated with your Azure OpenAI resource. During or after the sign-in workflow, select the appropriate directory, Azure subscription, and Azure OpenAI resource.#### DALL-E 3From the Azure OpenAI Studio landing page, select DALL·E playground (Preview) to use the image generation APIs. Select Settings near the top of the page and confirm that the Deployment dropdown has your DALL-E 3 deployment selected.#### DALL-E 2 (preview)From the Azure OpenAI Studio landing page, select DALL·E playground (Preview) to use the image generation APIs. Select Settings near the top of the page and confirm that the Deployment dropdown has the default DALL-E 2 choice selected.---
